  "name": "Nature’s Torrent",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/nature/tree-spirit-black.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>When a creature within 10 spaces of you takes Elemental damage, you can spend <strong>1</strong> <strong>AP</strong> as a <strong>Reaction</strong> to summon a torrent of nature.</p><p>The torrent fills a 3 Spaces Diameter Sphere centered on the target that lasts for 1 minute.</p><p>While creatures are within the area, they are have <strong>Vulnerable 1</strong> against the triggering damage type and have <strong>DisADV</strong> on Checks and Saves to resist being moved or knocked <strong>Prone</strong>.</p><p><strong>Ending Early:</strong> The torrent ends early if you use this Feature again, become Incapacitated, die, or choose to end it for free at anytime.</p>",
